Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.69,0:00:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別在意儘管忙得昏頭轉向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.60,0:00:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,微笑裝備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.57,0:00:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也自然high
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.40,0:00:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得意忘形的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.97,0:00:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有預約時間(硬比出V手勢)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.87,0:00:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女英雄駕到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.61,0:00:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡情的吃甜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.68,0:00:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘掉煩人的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.95,0:00:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ThankYou! 挖到寶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.82,0:00:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,招財貓招啊招(客人來吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.82,0:00:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定能進入你的內心殿堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.19,0:00:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩警報 (踩到地雷)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.13,0:00:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要有點刺激才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.50,0:00:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算吃海苔時噎到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.97,0:00:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是盯著攝影機看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.37,0:00:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擺出明星架式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.91,0:01:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題V手勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.74,0:01:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使 Rock'n'Roll
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.51,0:01:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老套的樂園(啊搖擺搖擺)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.71,0:01:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旋轉的宇宙也在跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.29,0:01:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火力全開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.22,0:01:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搖搖擺擺跳一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.63,0:01:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(啊搖擺搖擺)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.29,0:01:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都會變成天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.53,0:01:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.28,0:01:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，這種地方真的有遺失文明嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.85,0:01:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說嘛找了那麼久都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.68,0:01:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全揮棒落空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.92,0:01:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.29,0:01:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，你有沒有在聽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.16,0:01:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，我好渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.70,0:01:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們有完沒完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.96,0:02:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家難得認真的在工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.67,0:02:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們幹嘛像隻狗一樣吠個不停啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.80,0:02:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再稍微努力找一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.21,0:02:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，好可愛的小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.11,0:02:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是珍貴罕見的烏茲別克哈斯基犬的幼犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.95,0:02:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，你幾時買了這隻狗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.31,0:02:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼買不買的，我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.62,0:02:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這隻狗那麼名貴嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.35,0:02:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，即使是這麼小的幼犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.49,0:02:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一隻也要幾百萬吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.29,0:02:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，我想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.33,0:02:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是去年聖誕節爹地和媽咪買給我當過年的壓歲錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我完全忘光光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.90,0:02:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，這是我寶貝的長外套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.10,0:02:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這只臭狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.57,0:02:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我打死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.49,0:02:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小狗好可憐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把氣出在它身上真的很難看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是出氣，比較像解悶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.85,0:02:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都不對，是「狗走路撞到棒子」(原指「飛來橫禍」)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.92,0:02:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不實際踏出第一步的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.89,0:02:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論是好事還是壞事都不會發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.49,0:03:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來，走吧走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.93,0:03:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，請等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.20,0:03:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#07成語濃湯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.20,0:03:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.17,0:03:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了，找到遺失文明之前我們是不回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.31,0:03:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是要說這個啦\N找歸找，也要休息一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.32,0:03:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不太想走在這種滿是灰塵的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.59,0:03:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想看海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.89,0:03:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的，這群只會嘰嘰喳喳的傢伙真是沒有團隊精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.36,0:03:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這叫烏合之眾，你們知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘰嘰喳喳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.50,0:03:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.97,0:03:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.23,0:03:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以前就戴著這頂頭套嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們大家也有戴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.97,0:03:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.11,0:03:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.14,0:03:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們幾時戴上這個的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.61,0:03:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.61,0:03:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.29,0:04:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.29,0:04:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本是小事一樁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是強盜嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.16,0:04:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛好找他們來解解悶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.50,0:04:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂，你們這些小混混快點給我停車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 稍微拿你們來解悶一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.57,0:04:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不抵抗的話 我會稍微手下留情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.60,0:04:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是不抵抗的話 那就沒意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.84,0:04:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對喔 而且叫強盜乖乖聽話也很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.85,0:04:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全不聽人家講話的成語要怎麼說啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.18,0:04:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛，我記得是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.15,0:04:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對牛彈琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.99,0:04:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.39,0:04:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，真是豁然開朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.62,0:04:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，你們這幾個混帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.83,0:04:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們說誰是小混混啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.63,0:04:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老大，那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.80,0:04:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她在幹嘛啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.27,0:04:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，香草我在叫你耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.74,0:04:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺好詭異哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.28,0:04:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是趕快閃人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.71,0:05:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.95,0:05:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是說過了你們的對手是我們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.78,0:05:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.68,0:05:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不會是想放著女士不管掉頭就跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.65,0:05:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小混混先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.39,0:05:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然他們兩人要陪他們打，我們就無事可做羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就「高高掛起」，到一旁去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.73,0:05:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，薄荷，你好厲害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.93,0:05:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.44,0:05:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然偷藏著這種東西 這是犯規的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.17,0:05:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少囉嗦，你再碎碎念的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.94,0:05:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就用這台不論是什麼蟲只要一發就能打死兩次的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.82,0:05:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「超級殺蟲器」就能把你打成蜂窩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.48,0:05:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.78,0:05:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論是什麼蟲只要一發就能打死兩次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛?那個戴雞頭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.25,0:05:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的意思是當你們攻擊蘭花的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.39,0:05:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以開槍亂轟你們是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好恐怖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.67,0:05:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們知道這叫什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.40,0:05:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來告訴你們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.40,0:05:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給貓金幣(意指「無謂的浪費」)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.11,0:06:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來啊，來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發啊，發啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.32,0:06:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會變成這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.65,0:06:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣根本沒有解到悶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.85,0:06:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反而是賠了夫人又折兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.96,0:06:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?遺失文明的啟動?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.50,0:06:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊，剛才你們一連串莫名其妙的行動開始之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.24,0:06:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就感受到遺失文明啟動的能量了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該錯不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.84,0:06:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來這個遺失文明會直接執行人們說出的成語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.48,0:06:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又或許有興起這種現象的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.98,0:06:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那是什麼時候啟動的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.19,0:06:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根據我的推測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.82,0:06:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們之中的某人使用了遺失文明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.19,0:06:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並實踐了成語的含意進而啟動了開關吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.66,0:06:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有人知道是什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.23,0:07:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用遺失文明?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.93,0:07:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實踐成語的意義?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.14,0:07:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我打死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.91,0:07:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那個時候佛特丟出去的棒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.58,0:07:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼，所謂「燈塔下面最暗」就是這個意思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.22,0:07:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.85,0:07:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼各位要小心使用成語喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.72,0:07:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用釘子釘我們也知道啦(」用釘子釘」意指」提醒」)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.86,0:07:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.39,0:07:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會再說想休息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.34,0:07:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在天使隊應該團結一致將那根棒子拿回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.90,0:07:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，你們為什麼要把鳥頭脫掉呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.11,0:07:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家加油，快要到終點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.84,0:07:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，剛才那隻小狗好可愛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.88,0:07:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的小狗 是佛特用棒子丟它的那隻狗嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.85,0:07:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊，剛才還在這裏呢\N嘴裏還咬著一根棒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.25,0:07:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊 不過，現在與其找小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.69,0:08:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咬著一根棒子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.13,0:08:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊，就在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了，就是那隻小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.33,0:08:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.90,0:08:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好耶，棒子居然主動跑來找我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直就是飛蛾撲火嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，難道又亂用成語了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.24,0:08:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心，那是對岸的火災
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.68,0:08:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該跟我們無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.55,0:08:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，翅膀燒掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.35,0:08:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.49,0:08:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翅膀燒掉了算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的衣服、頭髮甚至連命都快被燒掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.33,0:08:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別吵了啦佛特，現在該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.33,0:08:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照這樣下去我們真的會被燒死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.63,0:08:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對喔，要先想個辦法處理這場火災
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.54,0:08:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦?怎麼辦?怎麼辦?怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼連蘭花都慌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.91,0:08:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找木乃伊的怎麼能變成木乃伊呢(原意指」一去不回」)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.68,0:08:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不是耍笨的時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.31,0:08:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定用個什麼成語就能解決這個狀況了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.28,0:08:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你難得腦袋這麼清楚，梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.69,0:09:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，例如說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.49,0:09:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,河童被河水沖走(原意指」任誰都會出錯」)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.86,0:09:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,河童?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.26,0:09:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,河童…  好耶，這樣說不定有救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.96,0:09:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,口若懸河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.96,0:09:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(覆水難收)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.47,0:09:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老年人的冷水(原意指「自不量力」)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.93,0:09:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡著時聽到水聲(原意指「晴天霹靂」)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.47,0:09:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等，澆錯地方了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.41,0:09:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡覺吧，晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.18,0:09:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,往燃燒的石頭潑水(原意指「杯水車薪」)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.95,0:09:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，薄荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.68,0:09:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷，你這混帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.56,0:09:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,河童
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.22,0:09:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的好可惜哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.92,0:09:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裏可惜了，根本造成反效果嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看看四周，你給我多看幾次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.13,0:09:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個豬頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.49,0:09:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，真的耶，嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.16,0:09:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿你的頭啦，我把你抓起來燒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.80,0:09:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的頭先燒起來了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.80,0:09:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!香草救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.17,0:09:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾麥德，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.77,0:09:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個時候要說那句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.27,0:09:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那句什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以毒攻毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.85,0:10:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.61,0:10:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪個頭啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.42,0:10:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心靜自然涼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.82,0:10:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有這一句啊，真不愧是香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.99,0:10:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，心靜自然涼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，完全不熱了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.99,0:10:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是如果燒光的話就沒有意義了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.17,0:10:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管這個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.63,0:10:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最重要的是要趕快離開這裏，不然真的會完蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.14,0:10:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是河童也快被烤乾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.31,0:10:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道就沒有什麼可以滅火的好成語嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.75,0:10:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，我們又見面了，可愛的小狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.22,0:10:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，我想到一句很棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.89,0:10:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什麼?佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.89,0:10:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人心就像秋天的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.40,0:10:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我懂了就是秋天下不停的雨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.17,0:10:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.14,0:11:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.47,0:11:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們幹嘛這麼拚命啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.21,0:11:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當天使隊也越當越累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.38,0:11:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(說的也是)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.42,0:11:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們解散吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.69,0:11:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪?大家到哪裏去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.23,0:11:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.23,0:11:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.10,0:11:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了把大家叫回來，所以你用了這個遺失文明是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.30,0:11:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，一心同體天使隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.31,0:11:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別鬧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.24,0:11:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是嘛，你要怎麼賠償我的身體?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋，笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.45,0:11:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該沒有」一心同體」這句成語吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.48,0:11:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猜拳十三奧義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.69,0:11:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始羅，剪刀石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,約定之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.82,0:11:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,約定之日是神聖的誓約，不允許任何人贏我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.40,0:12:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也開心一點嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.34,0:12:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的表情就好像是很討厭在這種地方工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.91,0:12:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的，我只是想起了往事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.85,0:12:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,往事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有個詩人曾經說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.22,0:12:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何，人生都是美好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.25,0:12:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敬你的回憶，乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.66,0:12:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那位詩人太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.83,0:12:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以怨恨點綴的人生才是真正的地獄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.93,0:12:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對，那起事件就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.60,0:12:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#08哀傷憎恨的凍豆腐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.88,0:12:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了約定時間還沒有出席會議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.75,0:12:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為她又睡過頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.88,0:12:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬萬沒想到居然發生了這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.72,0:12:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腦部受到毆打導致腦內出血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遭到鐵鎚之類的鈍器一擊斃命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.62,0:13:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，佛特我在叫你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.16,0:13:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請快點醒醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.16,0:13:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，究竟是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.90,0:13:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏不是外面的人能夠輕易進入的地區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.57,0:13:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，答案只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.44,0:13:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是身邊熟識的人幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，怎麼沒看到香草?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.91,0:13:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是香草?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.48,0:13:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，你在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.55,0:13:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們找遍了整個銀河終於找到你的藏身之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.42,0:13:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點出來吧，香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.26,0:13:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.56,0:13:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你究竟在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.57,0:13:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.21,0:13:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.38,0:13:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花，你看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.17,0:13:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草的遺言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.38,0:13:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾．．．優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.72,0:14:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是我，不是我殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.32,0:14:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是我殺的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.79,0:14:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那這個留言是怎麼回事?你要怎麼解釋?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.89,0:14:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼知道!一定是哪裏搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.36,0:14:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.10,0:14:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她不是我殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.87,0:14:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.97,0:14:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾麥德一直跟香草在一起或許他知道些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.55,0:14:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾麥德．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.62,0:14:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是第三個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.62,0:14:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兇手到底想幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，這個是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.13,0:14:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，你們好像誤會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.83,0:14:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誤會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.84,0:14:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道他的留言指的不是兇手嗎?(馬利普可可莫)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.81,0:14:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.91,0:14:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那他寫這個做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.98,0:15:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾麥德一定是叫我們替香草報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.45,0:15:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他早就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.48,0:15:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，香草和我們兩個其實是三姊弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧，怎麼可能．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.29,0:15:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我偶然發現的香草的日記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.56,0:15:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏面有寫著這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.23,0:15:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,7月28日，雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.47,0:15:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天在公園裏做了很久沒做的泥土丸子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.87,0:15:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙沙的苦苦的，我以前常做給弟弟們吃的泥土丸子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.81,0:15:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，我可愛的弟弟們馬利普與可可莫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.18,0:15:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在你們在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.12,0:15:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小時候吃過的那個泥土丸子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.46,0:15:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到居然是香草姊做給我們吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.39,0:15:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是難以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.33,0:15:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管你相不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.20,0:15:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草是跟我們流著同樣血緣的寶貝姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.60,0:15:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們絕對不會放過殺了她的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.17,0:16:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優，是你殺的嗎?梅爾優，是你殺的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.41,0:16:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不．．．不是的，不是我殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.14,0:16:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要說謊了，就算你說謊也馬上會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.35,0:16:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.71,0:16:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.88,0:16:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在飲料裏下毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.95,0:16:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼連他們兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.61,0:16:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優，難道真的是你?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.53,0:16:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是啦，不是我殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.96,0:16:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那到底是誰呢?這已經是第五個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.90,0:16:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.83,0:16:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在還不能逃啊，蘭花\N(佛特的日記)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.84,0:16:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們怎麼都來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.55,0:16:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.28,0:16:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們想把這個還給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.35,0:16:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是佛特的日記，為什麼要還給我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.85,0:16:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為是你弄丟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.19,0:16:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們在馬利普與可可莫遭人殺害的現場找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.30,0:16:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼啊，我根本聽不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.36,0:16:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝迷糊也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.53,0:17:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那稍微比他人來得認真嚴謹的個性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.47,0:17:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給你帶來了災難\N(烏丸千歲)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.74,0:17:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是薄荷·布拉曼修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.74,0:17:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，你還是太小看我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.21,0:17:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?你為什麼要殺死大家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.54,0:17:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這本日記裏寫的是真的\N佛特可是你的姊姊耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.69,0:17:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這正是原因所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.99,0:17:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我無法原諒殺死佛特姊的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.26,0:17:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是復仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.23,0:17:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優·櫻葉  殺死我姊姊的人就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.74,0:17:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我．．．我不是存心要殺她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.38,0:17:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果她．．．如果她沒說出那種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.48,0:17:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣啊?佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.85,0:17:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優·櫻葉特製的燉牛肉燴飯好不好吃啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.49,0:17:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是好吃到爆啊 這個牛肉洋蔥燴飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.72,0:18:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，那不是牛肉洋蔥燴飯 是燉牛肉燴飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個牛肉洋蔥燴飯真是棒透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.56,0:18:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優的牛肉洋蔥燴飯真的很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.40,0:18:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你說梅爾優的牛肉洋蔥燴飯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.27,0:18:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牛肉洋蔥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.82,0:18:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.25,0:18:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次真的很謝謝你 那個牛肉洋蔥燴飯真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.95,0:18:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.55,0:18:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是牛肉洋蔥燴飯是燉牛肉燴飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.59,0:18:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.86,0:18:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，說真的你真的很會做菜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.33,0:18:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩三下就能做出那麼好吃的牛肉洋蔥燴飯．．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.46,0:18:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.68,0:18:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係嘛叫什麼名字都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.71,0:18:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都一樣．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.95,0:18:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我回過神來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.21,0:18:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我手裏拿著醃醬菜的石頭打了佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.12,0:19:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是存心要殺她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.62,0:19:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是希望佛特明白燉牛肉燴飯不是牛肉洋蔥燴飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你實在太任性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.70,0:19:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我饒不了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.23,0:19:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.70,0:19:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算殺了佛特的人是梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.60,0:19:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你連香草他們都要殺死呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.21,0:19:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所謂以牙還牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.38,0:19:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.24,0:19:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，那三個人是梅爾優的兄弟姊妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.52,0:19:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?香草他們是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.42,0:19:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣?被命運捉弄的滋味如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.96,0:19:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很痛苦吧?很悲傷吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.49,0:19:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過別擔心，我是很善良的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.66,0:19:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我馬上就讓你去見那三個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.97,0:19:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流著血的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.30,0:19:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校，你怎麼會在這裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.50,0:19:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怨恨的連鎖效應  放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.44,0:19:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要彼此都還活著就會持續下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.14,0:19:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我要把它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.68,0:20:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼啊，中校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.61,0:20:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這樣!爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.79,0:20:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.92,0:20:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼大家都非死不可呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.99,0:20:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要去哪裏?梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.71,0:20:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要衝動，梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.34,0:20:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經是孤零零的一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.77,0:20:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你們，讓我死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.71,0:20:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，你不是一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人愛著你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.65,0:20:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優，對不起一直瞞著你到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.65,0:20:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我是你的媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.39,0:20:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這怎麼可能?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.96,0:20:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒騙你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.46,0:20:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是證據，我們的家譜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.56,0:20:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.76,0:20:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事實比小說更為奇特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.63,0:20:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我就是你的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.40,0:20:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.94,0:21:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我爸爸是華克中校吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.24,0:21:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是中校自己搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.54,0:21:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥總是這樣冒冒失失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.91,0:21:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.18,0:21:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，中校是我的哥哥也就是你的舅舅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.89,0:21:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷才是你真正的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.69,0:21:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你出生之後馬上就送給別人當養女了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.53,0:21:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也難怪你不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.90,0:21:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣明白了吧，梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.76,0:21:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是孤單一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.73,0:21:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人深深愛著你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.51,0:21:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是孤單一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.61,0:21:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人深深愛著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.83,0:22:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用怨恨點綴的人生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.80,0:22:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那這個事件什麼時候才要結束啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.77,0:22:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，接下來來演跟梅琳少校沒有血緣的妹妹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.42,0:22:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.46,0:22:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也愛米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.22,0:22:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也愛你，我最愛你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.69,0:22:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最愛米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.49,0:22:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為你放棄一切，身心都奉獻給你
